Movable Type Plugin: Test Extern Auth
-------------------------------------

Used to test the external authentication of MT with a plugin other then
the Enterprise addon - LDAP.

Installation
------------

as any other plugin, dump the plugins directory into MT's plugins

Add to your mt-config.cgi the following lines:

AuthenticationModule TestExtern
ExternalUserManagement 1

The user list is in "userlist.txt" file in the plugin directory. 
each line is a username,password record.


